node.text:
✨Work hard in silence and let your success be the noise.” ✨Competed my first ever lyrical solo @24sevendance by @madisonsmithhh_ from @matherdancecompanyofficial after 2 years of not competing a solo on stage. I was so scared and nervous that I would mess up, but my best Fríend @chachashen1 held my hand and whispered, “if you believe in me, I’ll believe in you! Love you Chacha! Of course I believe in you 💛Thank you @cristinascostumes for my beautiful costume. I love it! Thank you @mythreelittlesunshines for coming a day early to support me and do my hair. Thank you @madisonsmithhh_ , @autumnmiller & @alexisrowland__ for training me weekly to prepare me for my solo. Thank you @madisonsmithhh_ for choreographing an amazing solo!! 🙌🏻 Thank you to my family, @shannonmather1 , all my friends for showing me so much love after I got off stage!! Love you guys so much! 
#lyricalsolo #matherdancecompany #thankful
